headline: Tanzania president sworn in as opposition says hundreds killed in protests
description: Hassan, who was inaugurated for a second term on Monday, was elevated from vice president after the sudden death of her predecessor John Magufuli in 2021. headline: France's new 'unproductive wealth' tax reflects a limited adjustment

description: One year after his first fight in the men's category, the athlete stepped back into the ring on Saturday in Marseille. He reflects on his journey and criticizes the persistent misconceptions about gender in the world of sports.
